{"tid":820192,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜濤獲品牌青睞　率先跑出拍廣告","createTime":"2018-09-15T09:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T09:32:03.000Z","uid":113956,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c43de1c4edebb2fa027ea387ed9728cdd94a1fb7","tid":820192,"uid":113956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:28:27.000Z","msg":"大受姐姐姨姨們歡迎的19歲小鮮肉姜濤（姜B），早前傳出被三間唱片公司同時相中，打算簽他為旗下歌手。近日有護膚品牌率先找他拍攝廣告，由其中一位《全民造星》導師馬天佑擔任創作總監，馬天佑說：「今次係姜B第一次拍攝，佢有少少怕醜同緊張，但好可愛，拍攝廣告嗰排成日落大雨，但姜B一嚟到就出太陽。」"},{"pid":"9849b7fbd5262dc8740e678c97bdb81b881a3d43","tid":820192,"uid":102454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:30:05.000Z","msg":"姜B<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a0ff2666ef966f1b7f81525262af465f15a93e","tid":820192,"uid":113956,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"19歲仔<br />\n唱片公司瘋狂爭人<br />\n有一百萬袋又咁多廣告代言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4f7087fc0161d1847db9fe20a7abc5624d144c","tid":820192,"uid":19334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:32:03.000Z","msg":"好想幫姜B含....."}]}